    • startFuzzingSession

      public <R extends org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Resource> List<FuzzingLogEntry> startFuzzingSession(R resource)
      Description copied from interface: FuzzingContext
      This is the entry-point to a new Fuzzing-Session. In contrast to FuzzingContext.fuzzChild(java.lang.String, R), starting a new Fuzzing-Session must ensure, even for small probabilities, the fuzzer finds an entry-point.
